    ðŸ”¬ Research-backed: Implement 1 message/day free tier (a16z freemium optimization)
    
    Based on a16z research on freemium optimization:
    - Changed from 100 total messages to 1 message per day with daily reset
    - Creates the 'sting' that drives conversion after users experience the 'a-ha' moment
    - Daily reset ensures users feel the limitation every day, driving urgency
    
    Changes:
    - Added dailyMessagesUsed, dailyMessageResetDate, dailyMessageLimit to schema
    - Updated unifiedClientRepository with daily reset logic
    - Updated Stripe webhook for paid tier unlimited messages
    - Updated Chat.tsx banner with emotional daily limit messaging
    - Updated Home.tsx pricing card copy
    
    Research source: a16z.com/how-to-optimize-your-free-tier-freemium

